column2: Tips for using your new inbox
column3:
Tips for using your new inbox
[image: Gmail]

Welcome to your inbox
[image: Search]
Find emails fast
With the power of Google Search in your inbox, you can archive
<https://support.google.com/mail/answer/6576?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgmailwelc=
omeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>
all your email and find it
<https://support.google.com/mail/answer/6593?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgmailwelc=
omeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>
later in a flash. Your inbox stays tidy, and you never need to worry about
what to keep.
[image: Personalize]
Personalize East Point Group of Institutions Mail
Customize inbox backgrounds, email signatures, and other options in East
Point Group of Institutions Mail settings
<https://support.google.com/mail/answer/6562?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgmailwelc=
omeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>.
Review and adjust your privacy and security settings at My Account
<https://myaccount.google.com/>.
[image: Organize]
Organize your email
You can organize email with labels
<https://support.google.com/mail/answer/118708?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgmailwe=
lcomeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>,
which are like folders, but you can add more than one label to a message.
You can also use filters
<https://support.google.com/mail/answer/6579?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgmailwelc=
omeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>
to automatically sort and categorize messages as they come in.
[image: Social]
Chat and meet from your inbox
Chat with contacts and start video meetings with up to 25 people in Google
Hangouts
<https://support.google.com/hangouts/answer/3115176?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgm=
ailwelcomeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>
.

Get training and tips
Find Gmail guides, tips, cheat sheets, help switching from Microsoft=C2=AE
Outlook=C2=AE, and more at the G Suite Learning Center
<https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9259748?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgma=
ilwelcomeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>
.
Visit the Learning Center
<https://support.google.com/a/users/answer/9259748?hl=3Den&utm_source=3Dgma=
ilwelcomeemail&utm_medium=3Demail&utm_campaign=3Dgmailwelcome>

Happy emailing,
The Gmail Team

column2:
Second AWS Region in India, AWS Asia Pacific (Hyderabad) Coming
 Soon!
column3:
We are delighted to inform you that AWS is adding a second AWS Region in In=
dia which is expected to be operational in the second-half of 2022. The Asi=
a Pacific (Hyderabad) Region will be located in the state of Telangana.

Listen to Puneet Chandok, President AWS India and South Asia, AISPL on this=
 announcement
 <https://email.awscloud.com/b000mtZOLTYpMo8B000apNk>
Several of our customers have welcomed this announcement

=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D

=E2=80=9CWe trust the secure, proven and highly performant AWS platform to =
power RBL Bank=E2=80=99s digital transformation strategy, that is core to p=
roviding differentiated, personalized offerings for our customers. We are a=
lso leveraging the breadth and depth of AWS services including analytics, m=
achine learning, managed databases, compute, storage, serverless, security =
to accelerate innovation of new customer-facing products and services, whil=
e reducing our costs at the same time. The second region in India will allo=
ws us to further enhance redundancy and high availability by looking at exp=
anded disaster recovery solutions=E2=80=9D

Sankarson Banerjee, Chief Information Officer, RBL Bank Ltd.

=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D

=E2=80=9CAt Bajaj Allianz General Insurance we believe in pushing the bound=
aries of our customer obsession by having a healthy amalgamation of digital=
 into our way of doing business. We had envisaged that the next move in pro=
viding exceptional customer service will be a core transformation and chose=
 AWS as our preferred cloud provider to deploy our core digital policy admi=
nistration system. Along with this, AWS=E2=80=99s analytics and machine lea=
rning services will further help us to think out of the box and help innova=
te quickly thus remaining responsive to the evolving customer needs. We are=
 excited about the launch announcement of the second region in India, which=
 would further strengthen the availability and fault tolerance of our appli=
cations.=E2=80=9D

Tapan Singhel, MD & CEO, Bajaj Allianz General Insurance

=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D=3D

=E2=80=9CIn past few years, we have accelerated our digital journey and AWS=
 has helped us migrate our key applications to cloud. We leveraged AWS capa=
bilities in creating data platforms and exploring disruptive technologies h=
as enabled us to reach closer to the customer. We share a common goal of fo=
cusing on addressing customer needs and using technology to address them.=
=E2=80=9D

Parvez Mulla, Chief Operating Officer, HDFC Life

-----------------------------------

AWS Asia Pacific (Mumbai) Region was launched in 2016. Since then tens and =
thousands of Indian customers have adopted the AWS Cloud to build with incr=
eased flexibility, scalability and Security. AWS customers are already maki=
ng use of 77 Availability Zones across 24 infrastructure regions worldwide.=
 Today=E2=80=99s announcement brings the total number of global regions (op=
erational and in the works) up to 29.Visit the What's New Home Page to find=
 out about AWS services, features, and region expansion announcements as th=
ey are released.

Find out more =C2=BB
<https://aws.amazon.com/about-aws/global-infrastructure/?trk=3Dem_inv1_cta1=
>
